.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
House: farmhouse, gothic-revival, colonial, victorian, cape-cod
The people have 5 different hobbies: hiking, drawing, fishing, singing, card-games
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
5 different games are played: canasta, chess, whist, monopoly, domino
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: sports, adventure, musical, family, western

1. the person who's hobby is hiking is the farmhouse house
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person watching sports movies
3. the person playing canasta is the gothic-revival house
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person playing chess
5. the gothic-revival house is to the right of the colonial house
6. the old-gold-smoker is the person watching western movies
7. the kools-smoker is the victorian house
8. the person playing whist is in the middle
9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left
10. the chesterfields-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies
11. the kools-smoker is to the left or right of the person watching family movies
12. the lucky-strike-smoker is the person playing monopoly
13. the person who's hobby is card-games is the parliaments-smoker
14. the person who's hobby is singing is to the left or right of the cape-cod house

.:: Answer ::.
